# AGENTS.md

This repository uses a contract-first functional DAG workflow.

## Rules

1. Read the DAG/spec files before editing.
2. Do not implement before a contract and tests exist.
3. Keep DAG nodes pure and deterministic.
4. Keep filesystem, network, database, time, randomness, process environment, and hidden global state outside pure nodes.
5. Do not change public interfaces unless explicitly requested.
6. Do not edit outside the assigned node or conversion slice unless the user asks.
7. Do not weaken tests to pass.
8. If a contract is impossible or underspecified, propose a contract change instead of silently modifying it.
9. Run node-level and full verification before finishing.
10. Explain what changed and how it was verified.

